nodes.text: The Dellalt Project was the name given to the archaeological excavation and study of the Queen of Ranroon, the ancient treasure ship of the pre-Republic galactic ruler Xim the Despot, which was discovered deep within a system of underground vaults on Dellalt in 1 BBY. The endeavor was headed by lead researcher S. V. Skynx, a renowned Xim historian who played a key role in uncovering the lost treasure.
